item.title: How can i take out the ancients tab & make you start on ancients?
item.dc:creator: @slomifier slomifier
item.description:
@slomifier wrote:

ok, im typing on my psp right now, so I cant give you the code. dont lose hope, ill get you the code when i can get on my pc.[br][size=1]Posted on: May 21, 2007, 08:31:45 AM[/size][hr]Ok, Im on my PC now. Now this isnet a very descriptive TuT, and it’s tiny, but you should be able to figure it out…:

setSidebarInterface(6, 1151); //magic tab (Modern = 1151);

setSidebarInterface(7, 1151); //magic tab (Modern = 1151);

setSidebarInterface(6, 12855); //magic tab (Ancient = 12855);

setSidebarInterface(7, 12855); //magic tab (Ancient = 12855);

Ok, im not exactly sure what you mean, so i’ll tell you what these do, and you can figure it out from there.

The first one sets the modern mage tab, to modern mage.

The second one sets the modern mage tab to ancient mage

The third one sets the ancients mage tab to modern mage

The forth one sets the ancients tab to ancients magic.

So, if I understand what your trying to do, find your login code, and add one of the above codes to the login code.

I hope that helped.
